com.pholser.junit.quickcheck.generator

Class IntegralGenerator<T extends Number>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.pholser.junit.quickcheck.generator.Generator<T>
      • com.pholser.junit.quickcheck.generator.IntegralGenerator<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - type of values this generator produces
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Gen<T>, Shrink<T>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BigIntegerGenerator, ByteGenerator, IntegerGenerator, LongGenerator, ShortGenerator

    public abstract class IntegralGenerator<T extends Number>
extends Generator<T>
    Base class for generators of integral types, such as int and BigInteger. All numbers are converted to/from BigInteger for processing.
